{"tid":1673544,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一步一步進迫，原來香港人咁易對付？","createTime":"2019-10-24T16:58:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-24T17:21:08.000Z","uid":81236,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"53c0d5f221376fac242b0775a785870489106e2b","tid":1673544,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T16:58:28.000Z","msg":"先係蒙面法，帶個口罩都要拉<br />\n香港人又真係唔帶喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後唔批不反對，係咪都話你非法集會<br />\n香港人又真係唔出喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家連貼個文宣都又鎖又拉？<br />\n想問下又拉啲咩？高調拉低調放？<br />\n香港人係咪會縮返埋屋企就算數<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n大家無理由輸比班垃圾毅進仔<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">大家好似忘記左文宣既影響</span></span><br />\n<br />\n好多唔上連登/tg既一家大細，唔上網既老弱婦孺都係睇佢地<br />\n文宣係呢幾個月令到香港人了解到香港暴政同埋警暴係萬惡之源<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">文宣既威力絕對唔比勇武遜色</span></span><br />\n<br />\n運動可以持續文宣組既製作同埋貼連儂牆係勞苦功高<br />\n仲有唔同group為大家製作同埋收集全港文宣<br />\n文宣製作後好需要大家既親力親為將香港人既努力發揚光大<br />\n唔好浪費佢地一片苦心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n入文宣tg group，成為文宣既一份子<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係唔同社交媒體share開去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n中文文宣谷<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/hkstandstrong_promo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkstandstrong_promo&d=wRNUG5%2F8jzvhtT%2FDMFjpNoE4T4y%2BYV5jPOnVoTo%2FPYs%3D&h=9b3bc915\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkstandstrong_promo</a><br />\n<br />\n英文文宣channel<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/hkstandstrong_promo_int\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkstandstrong_promo_int&d=wRNUG5%2F8jzvhtT%2FDMFjpNoE4T4y%2BYV5jPOnVoTo%2FPYs%3D&h=7d518675\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkstandstrong_promo_int</a><br />\n<br />\n係學校公司印定先<br />\n一齊係未有活動既平日<br />\n係自己區樓下連儂牆貼下文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1feb0ae5a9713a2adfe06ee2220ec92a3d76c496","tid":1673544,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T16:58:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gv2xOLu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgv2xOLu.jpg&h=a9eb1a8f&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"abce9eca09e4177fcc9a743f5bc1d2d12a09897b","tid":1673544,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T16:59:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/senatorleahy/status/1184865122977746945?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsenatorleahy%2Fstatus%2F1184865122977746945%3Fs%3D21&d=wRNUG5%2F8jzvhtT%2FDMFjpNoE4T4y%2BYV5jPOnVoTo%2FPYs%3D&h=557038b9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsenatorleahy%2Fstatus%2F1184865122977746945%3Fs%3D21&h=1ba2513b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/senatorleahy/status/1184865122977746945?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n依個Senator 未Cosponsor 條Bill<br />\n得百幾retweet rate<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc6060caa8cf24c14874963b971e3177f1e9315b","tid":1673544,"uid":182195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T17:01:35.000Z","msg":"推 鍾意睇分析文<br />\n都值得比更多人睇<br />\n可以討論/反思"},{"pid":"75425b0ce4ad365c1e6d47407163ea4487f4cbe8","tid":1673544,"uid":48212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T17:01:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25d39196b4f5e934c66f71f92a9e83c9b037da52","tid":1673544,"uid":182195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T17:02:20.000Z","msg":"香港人反抗唔係口號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"